Spells
Necromancers can access a list of their spells with the ~>necspells<~
command. Additionally, they may list only those spells which are
available to them by using the 'avail' argument. In addition to these
abilities, they have access to the ~>necro<~, ~>necros<~, ~>nechist<~,
and ~>nritual<~ commands. Help for these commands can be accessed through
using: help <command>, where <command> is the ability's syntax, such as
'help nspray'.
